overview: Hartono, a administration staff of "Partai ASU" (Anggaran Semuanya Untukmu) is a innocent one who always be used by Partai ASU to be nominated as a President Candidate. This case done because lastest President Candidate from Partai ASU be arrested by KPK because the corruption case. Then Hartono realize that he was only used as a puppet of the leaders and continue to cover their crimes. In the middle of numerous threads, Hartono tried to follow her inner voice
title: Capres (Calo Presiden)
